channel.title: Won't be as active
channel.description: Hey everyone, I'm not sure if this is against the rules but I just want to let you all know that I won't be as active because my computer got fried over night. I need to stop leaving my computer on so much. Now, my computer tower is useless so I'm keeping my hard drive and my processor but the rest is junk. So with this being the case, I have to use my family computer which EVERYONE uses so I just won't be getting on as much for pretty much a year, or until I buy new components and windows 7 for a new computer that me and my friend will work on. Aaron, sorry I won't be able to get on RSPS Universe much. I'll get a new computer eventually. See you all every now and then! Bye! :/
